alination for seawater and brackish water, recycle and zero liquid discharge services; and operation and maintenance contracts, products and process audits, health check-ups, upgradation of existing plants, and on-site support, as well as spares and services. It serves industrial clusters, refineries, coal, sand processing plant, non-ferrous industries, oil and gas, thermal and hydro power plants, steel plants, sugar and allied industries, and desalination industries. Triveni Engineering & Industries Limited was incorporated in 1932 and is headquartered in Noida, India."}}